<h2 class="n">Men's Ministries</h2>
<p class="highlight">The men of Portland Christian Center, located in Portland, Oregon, are committed to promoting, encouraging and developing these areas of ministry to men: Evangelism, Spiritual Growth, Fellowship and Service to others.</p>
<p>Our programs, activities, sporting events and prayer groups are designed to show that Christian men have a way of life to be desired.</p>
<blockquote>"Be on your guard; stand firm in the faith; be men of courage; be strong. Do everything in love."<br /><strong>1 Corinthians 16:13-14</strong></blockquote>
